summary: AN ORDINANCE, relating to a vehicular and pedestrian tunnel under the alley between 6th Avenue and 7th Avenue, north of Stewart Street, amending Ordinance 119508, as amended by Ordinance 121855, updating the insurance and bond requirements, and amending the annual fee; renewing the term of the permit to Plaza 600 Building L.L.C.; providing for acceptance of the permit and conditions; and ratifying and confirming certain prior acts.
